{"title":"海滩上的孩子","authors":["黄东成"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":7,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海滩上的孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄东成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄昏。海滩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个天真的孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹲在夕照里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全神贯注在堆沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一捧，他一捧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆积着他们幻想中的高山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆一座爷爷走过的庐山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆一座爸爸走过的黄山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆一座妈妈说最高最高的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有南天门的泰山……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涨潮了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海水悄悄爬上沙滩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞒过孩子的警觉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫过南天门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将一座座幻想哗地冲坍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲坍了精心构筑的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座座童真的峰峦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个孩子蹒跚地奔跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不让海水追着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换一个地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又蹲下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续堆积他们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幻想的纯真"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙垒的宫殿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而我知道，海水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在不断上涨……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}